# Audiobooks Directory

This directory contains audio files for books and novels.

## Organization:
- Create subdirectories for each book using book ID
- Support for multiple languages (en/ur subdirectories)
- Chapter-based organization for long works

## Structure:
```
books/
├── {book-id}/
│   ├── en/
│   │   ├── full.mp3 (complete audiobook)
│   │   ├── chapter-01.mp3
│   │   ├── chapter-02.mp3
│   │   └── ...
│   └── ur/
│       ├── full.mp3
│       ├── chapter-01.mp3
│       └── ...
```

## Supported Formats:
- MP3 (recommended)
- WAV
- OGG
- AAC
